title: ISic000923. I.Sicily inscription 000923
body:
Facsimile Images

Ἐπαφρό<δ>ειτος
ἐτελεύτησεν
μην(ὶ) Δεκεν-
βρί{α}ῳ ((alpha)) Ἰ(ησοῦς) (Χριστὸ)ς ((omega))

Apparatus criticus

Text after transcription of Orsi (correcting Carini / Kaibel)

English translation

Epaphrodeitos passed away in the month of December. ((Alpha)) Jesus Christ ((Omega))

commentary
